{"tid":1794099,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"旅發局首辦除夕倒數抽獎","createTime":"2019-12-23T01:16:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-31T02:14:50.000Z","uid":241115,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bfa8e339ff2efd0069cbb374ec433ea2bb3a2f53","tid":1794099,"uid":241115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:16:25.000Z","msg":"旅發局今年除夕夜倒數不會舉辦煙花匯演，但會在午夜舉行加強版「幻彩詠香江」及舉辦大抽獎，當晚市民和<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">在港旅客</span></strong>可以在旅發局網頁參加抽獎。<br />\n<br />\n旅發局節目及旅遊產品拓展總經理洪忠興說，抽獎分兩部分，包括玩小遊戲贏取100元超市禮券，名額2萬個，以及壓軸大抽獎。<br />\n<br />\n頭獎有10個，為航空公司向每名中獎者送出4套來回香港與自選目的地的經濟艙機票，其中兩套讓得獎者贈予外地親友來港。旅發局表示，希望透過頭獎在2020年讓20位港人外遊，並帶20位親友回港。另外其他禮品亦與本港旅遊業有關，包括主題樂園入場券和酒店住宿。<br />\n<br />\n抽獎在除夕下午6時至晚上11時半進行，禮品總值超過400萬元，頭獎得主會在當晚的倒數特備節目上公布。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499092-20191223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499092-20191223.htm&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwZSOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=243f9279\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1499092-20191223.htm&h=202f5b80\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1499092-20191223.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪又係抽比大陸旅客 每個登記帳號可無限次玩遊戲，直至贏到現金卷為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5d399c3208eafacfff6fd1533d57849e19bf9f","tid":1794099,"uid":108571,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:20:30.000Z","msg":"屌 全部參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得獎係自己人都開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重要既係唔想啲藍既繼續帶大陸人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢可能目的想益新移民大陸人同藍絲廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d21f85e3a5406d4d6dfe2df58a3874065142506","tid":1794099,"uid":241115,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T01:22:11.000Z","msg":"全部人一齊參加 唔好比藍老抽中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712f9e4c65a292c74e51bd33fbdf72ff061b2702","tid":1794099,"uid":38145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:11:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9db66751b08b2d2ceb4817cb63098f24907096d4","tid":1794099,"uid":241115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:08:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313fe5297df46a519cde4a37da090665d31196c9","tid":1794099,"uid":241115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:08:40.000Z","msg":"冇人理"},{"pid":"428b79386b47f81e47246e6a219091cd2f01106e","tid":1794099,"uid":241115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:08:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db0ada6c6b121332bd3fa1ef2319474a971af146","tid":1794099,"uid":241115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"咪L益大陸人 同藍絲"},{"pid":"5fa82658d53559d70ef35b324728eea25b7641eb","tid":1794099,"uid":24570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"遊客都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7793f1368b91aa4da5dbba08e9d8145b83b236","tid":1794099,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:13:35.000Z","msg":"國際文宣：一齊同全世界講有呢個抽獎，準時6點vpn入"},{"pid":"d45a1e8545003648064d268eb14f8a1b4075493d","tid":1794099,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T02:14:41.000Z","msg":"政府似會做馬"},{"pid":"fb5e369d71fd6b22034728eb2